Old APi is working 24/06/2024 so i teach new version api and how can use :-

Build a Message Request:

{
  "message": {
    "token": "<REGISTRATION_TOKEN>",
    "notification": {
      "title": "Hello",
      "body": "World"
    }
  }
}


Send the Requset APi :
POST https://fcm.googleapis.com/v1/projects/<PROJECT_ID>/messages:send
PROJECT_ID = Firebase Project Id


Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>
Access Token : go to Google cloud  and go to service account and 
first check your create service account is created or not if not created then create manually after create go to inside and go to key and create a new key 
you show key copy and paste access token place




